      "verse_key": "101:1",
      "text_ar": " ٱلْقَارِعَةُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "The Calamity!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6159,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 2,
      "verse_key": "101:2",
      "text_ar": "مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "What is the Calamity?"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6160,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 3,
      "verse_key": "101:3",
      "text_ar": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Ah, what will convey unto thee what the Calamity is!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6161,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 4,
      "verse_key": "101:4",
      "text_ar": "يَوْمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلْفَرَاشِ ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "A day wherein mankind will be as thickly-scattered moths"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6162,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 5,
      "verse_key": "101:5",
      "text_ar": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلْجِبَالُ كَٱلْعِهْنِ ٱلْمَنفُوشِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And the mountains will become as carded wool."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6163,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 6,
      "verse_key": "101:6",
      "text_ar": "فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Then, as for him whose scales are heavy (with good works),"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6164,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 7,
      "verse_key": "101:7",
      "text_ar": "فَهُوَ فِى عِيشَةٍ رَّاضِيَةٍ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "He will live a pleasant life."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6165,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 8,
      "verse_key": "101:8",
      "text_ar": "وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "But as for him whose scales are light,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6166,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 9,
      "verse_key": "101:9",
      "text_ar": "فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٌ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "A bereft and Hungry One will be his mother,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 6167,
      "surah": 101,
      "ayah": 10,
      "verse_key": "101:10",
      "text_ar": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Ah, what will convey unto thee what she is! -"
    },
